# Notion database reference

## People databases
- Staff: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
- Candidates: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

## Finance databases
- Payables: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
- Invoices: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

## Projects databases
- Projects: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 (Data Source: collection://00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000)
- Clients: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

## Key pages
- Dashboard: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

## Query patterns
- Use Page ID for notion-fetch (reading a specific page)
- Use Data Source (collection://) URL for notion-search and notion-create-pages
- Filter by Status = Active for current items
